Dear Ms. Rivera,

This is your annual reminder from the U.S. Department of Veterans Affairs regarding open enrollment for your benefits election.

Open enrollment window: November 1, 2026 through December 15, 2026.

If you wish to change your current elections (pharmacy tier, dental supplemental, or spousal coverage), please log in to your VA account by December 15. If you take no action, your current elections will roll forward automatically for the 2027 benefit year.

You may access your account at the URL on your annual mailer. If you have questions, contact your regional VA office.

Please do not reply to this email; this mailbox is not monitored.

- VA Outreach (automated reminder)

